INTERFERON SCIENCES, INC. REPORTS THIRD QUARTER RESULTS

Interferon Sciences, Inc.  (NASDAQ-IFSC) has reported a net
loss of $1,972,000 for the quarter ended September 30, 1995,
as compared to a net loss of $4,367,000 for the same period in
1994. The decreased loss results primarily from the write-off
of prepaid royalty expenses to Hoffmann-La Roche of
approximately $2,000,000 during the third quarter of 1994.



