GB 2 289 050 A Published: November 8, 1995; Filed: May 5, 1995; Priority:
May 6, 1994
The Hong Kong University of Science and Technology, Kowloon, (Hong Kong)
   The present invention provides a cellobiase produced by Cellulomonas
