EPO 681 026 A1 Published: November 8, 1995; Filed: February 29, 1988;
Priority: March 2, 1987
Whitehead Institute for Biomedical Research, Cambridge, MA (US)
Recombinant mycobacterial vaccine vehicles capable of expressing foreign
