Service and Health Care Financing Administration
programs.  It is recommended for use in all clinical
settings for health care providers, administrators,
health care facilities, medical researchers, and
others.  The CD-ROM is DOS, Windows, and Macintosh
compatible, and contains Folio(R) search and retrieval
software.  System requirements for DOS or Windows: DOS
5.0 or higher, 4 Mb Ram, 6 Mb hard disk space.  System
requirements for Macintosh: 68030 or higher with System
7 or higher, 8 Mb RAM, 6 Mb hard disk space.

