1996
 -- The longest steel arch bridge  was built over the Niagara River.
 -- Work began on the Williamsburg bridge in New York City.
 -- The Chicago Sanitary and Ship Canal was 77% complete.
 -- The 386-ft Park Row building in New York was tallest of all.

