Catalyst and process improvements cited

from CHEMICAL BUSINESS NEWSBASE, 12 Nov 1996

Ref: Chemical Engineering Progress, Oct 1996, Vol. 92, No. 10, Pg. 28

BP Chemicals Inc and Lurgi Ol-Gas-Chemie GmbH, Frankfurt have jointly
developed improvements to their Geminox BDO process used to manufacture
1,4-butanediol and derivatives.

Improved catalysis and process flexibility now provide more than 94%
1,4-butanediol yields for the process.

