US oxygenates: producers join forces to support US mandate

from CHEMICAL BUSINESS NEWSBASE, 12 Nov 1996

Ref: European Chemical News, 4 Nov 1996, Vol. 66, No. 1739, Pg. 10

US producers of MTBE and ethanol are to work together to oppose any
