EniChem: SBC growth by end use

from CHEMICAL BUSINESS NEWSBASE, 12 Nov 1996

Ref: European Rubber Journal, Nov 1996, Vol. 178, No. 10, Pg. 42

EniChem Elastomeri has total capacity for styrene block copolymers of
