Copesul increases ethylene capacity

from CHEMICAL BUSINESS NEWSBASE, 12 Nov 1996

Ref: Gazeta Mercantil, 11 Oct 1996, No. 20.939, Pg. Relatorio 1

Original text in PORTUGUESE

Copesul, the raw materials centre in the Rio Grande do Sul
