from CHEMICAL BUSINESS NEWSBASE, 12 Nov 1996

Ref: International Pest Control, Sep-Oct 1996, Vol. 38, No. 5, Pg. 152-153

United Phosphorus Ltd is producing aluminium phosphide, formulated
