ethical manufacturers (up 2.1%) and Yen 29.0 bn for 5 of the OTC
manufacturers (up 2.5%).

Combined investment in plant and equipment was Yen 40 bn for 12 of the
ethical manufacturers and Yen 20. 8 bn for the OTC manufacturers.

