Matra Plast to open PC sheet facility in Long Sault, ON

from CHEMICAL BUSINESS NEWSBASE, 12 Nov 1996

Ref: Plastics News, 26 Aug 1996, Vol. 8, No. 26, Pg. 1

In Jan 1997, production is due to be started by Matra Plast Inc at the
first of its two new polycarbonate sheet extrusion lines to be
installed in Long Sault, ON.

The facility has been acquired from Dominion Textile Ltd.

