Gist-brocades: nutrition and health: new product development for a growing
market

from CHEMICAL BUSINESS NEWSBASE, 12 Nov 1996

Ref: The Gist, Autumn 1996, No. 66, Pg. 6-7

Nutrition is a target area for an increasing number of food and
pharmaceutical companies wishing to focus on the development of foods
for specific population segments.

The recent major product developments of Gist-brocades in this area are
outlined.

Gist-brocades has developed a proprietary large-scale production
