Hyosung-BASF Co to increase capacity

from CHEMICAL BUSINESS NEWSBASE, 12 Nov 1996

Ref: Plastics News, 30 Sep 1996, Vol. 8, No. 31, Pg. 9

By Oct 1997, capacity at Hyosung-BASF Co's 88 M lb/y ABS facility in
Ulsan is to be raised to 418 M lb/y, making it the largest such unit in
