<HR>
<A NAME = "50"></A>Copyright
CHEMICAL ENGINEERING via NewsNet
January 1996   Vol. 103, No. 

Dresser Industries, Inc. (Dallas, Tex.) makes senior management changes:

Dresser Industries, Inc. (Dallas, Tex.) makes senior management changes:
William Bradford, previously president and chief operating officer, has
been named president and chief executive officer.
   Donald Vaughn, president of Dresser's Engineering Services subsidiary,
M.W. Kellogg, Inc., is appointed executive vice president.
