MOLTEN METAL TECHNOLOGY PLANT COMMISSIONED

Scientific Ecology Group, Inc. (Oak Ridge, Tenn.)and Molten Metal
Technology, Inc. (Waltham, Mass) have commissioned their Quantum-CEP plant
(CE, January, 1995, p. 55). The unit is capable of processing 130,000
ft3/yr of radioactive ion-exchange resins.

