process design, production and project management.

Dale A. Seiberling is President and Principal of Seiberling Associates,
Inc. (11415 Main Street, Roscoe, IL 61073; Tel: 815/623-7311), an
engineering firm specializing in process and CIP design. He received B.S.
and M.S. degrees in dairy technology from Ohio State University. He has
over 40 years of process and CIP engineering experience. He lectures
extensively on CIP and has published many articles and sections of books on
CIP technology and applications.

