balance of the system, by considering the vapor from the last effect.
   W = En[ln + Cw (tn twi)] / (two-twi) (12)
Solving Equation 8 for SA, and combining it with Equations 2, 3, 4 and 5
gives:

(This equation is not available electronically. Please see January 1996,
