c  For fabric filters, each quarterly value shown is the average of the
Producer Price Indexes for the three months in question.
d  For mechanical collectors, each quarterly value shown is the average of
the Producer Price Indexes for the three months in question.

Note: For a detailed explanation of the development and use of the VAPCCI,
see Chem. Eng., December 1995, pp. 88-95.

